{
  "page": "Wroth of the Dragonlords",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Wroth of the Dragonlords</b></i> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">mummer</a>'s play written by <a href=\"/index.php/Phario_Forel\" title=\"Phario Forel\">Phario Forel</a>. It is the first play Forel ever wrote.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The play presumably deals with the history of the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a> between the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a>, in which the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonlord\" title=\"Dragonlord\">dragonlords</a> crushed <a href=\"/index.php/Garin_the_Great\" title=\"Garin the Great\">Garin the Great</a>'s army with their <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> In the play, Prince Garin gives a speech on the eve of battle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wroth_of_the_Dragonlords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wroth_of_the_Dragonlords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Izembaro\" title=\"Izembaro\">Izembaro</a>, the King of the Mummers, quotes Prince Garin from <i>Wroth of the Dragonlords</i> the night he and his group of mummers at <a href=\"/index.php/The_Gate\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Gate\">the Gate</a> are set to perform <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Bloody_Hand\" title=\"The Bloody Hand\">The Bloody Hand</a></i>, also written by Phario Forel.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wroth_of_the_Dragonlords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It shall go ill for any man who fails me.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Izembaro\" title=\"Izembaro\">Izembaro</a>, quoting Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Garin_the_Great\" title=\"Garin the Great\">Garin the Great</a>'s line from the play</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wroth_of_the_Dragonlords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Mercy-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Mercy_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Mercy (The Winds of Winter)\">Mercy</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: Ten Thousand Ships.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403163246\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 196/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8975/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2655/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 874/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1411/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   10.818      1 -total\n 38.47%    4.162      1 Template:Ref\n 24.92%    2.696      1 Template:Ref/core\n 18.81%    2.035      1 Template:References\n 17.92%    1.939      1 Template:Warning/twow\n 13.40%    1.450      1 Template:Warning\n 10.24%    1.108      1 Template:Quote\n  8.85%    0.957      1 Template:Mbox\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:16923-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403163246 and revision id 297444\n -->\n",
